data.description: Introducing a charming home at 3259 Beloit Terrace, North Port, FL.  This inviting home features a well-designed split floor plan, offering three bedrooms and two bathrooms for ample space and privacy.  The master bedroom is a highlight, complete with a spacious walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom, providing a comfortable retreat.  The property boasts a vinyl-fenced yard, offering both privacy and a touch of aesthetic appeal.  One of the standout features is the screened rear porch lanai, providing a perfect spot for relaxation and outdoor enjoyment.  Additionally, the home includes a large great room, creating a versatile space for various activities and gatherings.  The home benefits from a neighborhood with a range of attractions where residents can explore the natural beauty of the area, with parks and outdoor spaces nearby.  Additionally, the area offers convenient access to local schools, shopping centers, and dining options.  This listing presents an excellent opportunity for those seeking a cozy yet well-appointed home in a desirable North Port location.  With a thoughtful split floor plan, a master bedroom retreat, and a spacious great room, this property offers both comfort and versatility.  Ideal for first-time buyers, investors, or those looking for a second home, it combines practicality with charm.
